<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7290] Change schemaless _text and copyField</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7290</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;schemaless configs should remove copyField to _text&lt;br/&gt;
or at least change _text name.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://markmail.org/message/v6djadk5azx6k4gv&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://markmail.org/message/v6djadk5azx6k4gv&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This default led to bad indexing performance.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
